## **Q82 (Time & Work)**

A can complete a work in **15 days** and B in **25 days**. Working together, they complete the work in:

A) 9.375 days

B) 10 days

C) 11 days

D) 12 days

✅ **Answer:** **A) 9.375 days**

### **Explanation**

[
\frac1{15}+\frac1{25}=\frac8{75}
]

Time

[
=\frac{75}{8}=9.375\text{ days}
]

⭐ **CDS Short Trick**

[
\text{Time}=\frac{ab}{a+b}
]

